      "content": "i hear you about the doctor but honestly i just want a more natural way to handle it. if i'm really disciplined about it and take like 3000mg of garlic extract and drink a large spinach smoothie every single morning, that should theoretically keep my levels steady right? if i stay consistent then i shouldn't need the blood tests as much, right? it just seems like a much cleaner way to do things.",
